{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-beifeng-005__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-beifeng-005", "source_id": "guofeng-beifeng-005__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·邶風·005.1", "text_original": "終風且暴，顧我則笑，謔浪笑敖，中心是悼。", "text_normalized": "終風且暴，顧我則笑，謔浪笑敖，中心是悼。", "notes": "終風 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-beifeng-005__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-beifeng-005", "source_id": "guofeng-beifeng-005__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·邶風·005.2", "text_original": "終風且霾，惠然肯來，莫往莫來，悠悠我思。", "text_normalized": "終風且霾，惠然肯來，莫往莫來，悠悠我思。", "notes": "終風 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-beifeng-005__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-beifeng-005", "source_id": "guofeng-beifeng-005__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·邶風·005.3", "text_original": "終風且曀，不日有曀，寤言不寐，願言則嚏。", "text_normalized": "終風且曀，不日有曀，寤言不寐，願言則嚏。", "notes": "終風 Chinese stanza 3."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-beifeng-005__004__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-beifeng-005", "source_id": "guofeng-beifeng-005__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·邶風·005.4", "text_original": "曀曀其陰，虺虺其靁，寤言不寐，願言則懷。", "text_normalized": "曀曀其陰，虺虺其靁，寤言不寐，願言則懷。", "notes": "終風 Chinese stanza 4."}
